{"tid":2382721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★下月起綜援生果金調高2.7%　高額長生津加至$3815","createTime":"2021-01-27T12:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T09:54:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f268c272e84502e232bb57c8f2e355dc899c7162","tid":2382721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"社會福利署今日（27日）公布，由下月1日起，按社會保障援助物價指數的變動，調高綜合社會保障援助（綜援）計劃的標準項目金額，以及公共福利金計劃下俗稱生果金的高齡津貼、長者生活津貼及傷殘津貼金額2.7%，其中一般長生津由2770港元，調高至2845港元，增加75港元；高額長生津則由3715港元，調高100港元至3815港元。此外，租金津貼最高金額亦按租金指數調高1.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210127/bkn-20210127163619605-0127_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210127%2Fbkn-20210127163619605-0127_00822_001.html&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=ff680b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210127/bkn-20210127163619605-0127_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"df2106e0e67dca0e15771ebedc1df14c7aeb8d2e","tid":2382721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664d29b88ba0b6cd797cfc3bd25fcfc3ae6fb677","tid":2382721,"uid":357710,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f268c272e84502e232bb57c8f2e355dc899c7162","tid":2382721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"社會福利署今日（27日）公布，由下月1日起，按社會保障援助物價指數的變動，調高綜合社會保障援助（綜援）計劃的標準項目金額，以及公共福利金計劃下俗稱生果金的高齡津貼、長者生活津貼及傷殘津貼金額2.7%，其中一般長生津由2770港元，調高至2845港元，增加75港元；高額長生津則由3715港元，調高100港元至3815港元。此外，租金津貼最高金額亦按租金指數調高1.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/h